title: Are you Looking For 55+ Community? Take a Look on This one!! 2/2 Unit
posting_body: ['SENIOR COMMUNITY.', 'Beautifully renovated 2x2 Villa.', 'New floors in the living area and bedrooms.', 'Charming wood beamed ceilings & renovated kitchen.', 'Tiled kitchen.', 'Courtyard entry & large screened patio.', 'No upstairs neighbors!', '1 assigned parking.', 'Washer/dryer inside unit.', 'Gated community.', 'Many amenities.', 'MUST BE 55+ YEARS OLD.', 'Association requires: $200 Deposit, 650+ CREDIT, no bankruptcies & evictions last 7 years, no commercial vehicles.', '1 pet (no aggressive breeds/ -25lbs).', 'Landlord requires: Monthly income 2.5x rent.', '1st month + 2 months Security Deposit.', 'Other charges required by Association: $25 ID fee + $25 refundable deposit + $25 barcode per car + $25 refundable deposit.', 'Move-in process takes up to thirty days, and the Association offers a rush fee to reduce the delay to 10 biz days.', ' ***', 'Please Text Message DALIT to ***', 'show contact info', '***', 'For  Details & Photos Of This Property***Brought to you by Dalit Rosenfeld at La Rosa Realty, Greater Fort Lauderdale.', '****', 'show contact info', '***', 'For more Properties HERE!', '<URL>']
